msg: Removed the AbstractIdentifiedObject.setNames(Collection<ReferenceIdentifier>) because whether that method
was invoked or not was JAXB-implementation dependent. Instead design AbstractIdentifiedObject in a way that
should work the same on all supported JDK versions.
